---
---

<section id="cenik">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Ceník</h2>
      <p>Žádné skryté poplatky – vždy domluvíme cenu předem</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-cards">

      <!-- Řemesla -->
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <div class="pricing-category-title">Řemesla</div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">1 pracovník</span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value">700 Kč / hod</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">2 pracovníci</span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value">1 400 Kč / hod</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">3 pracovníci</span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value">2 100 Kč / hod</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">Pohotovostní výjezd <sup>*</sup></span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value">2 500 Kč</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">Použití speciální techniky</span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value muted">individuální</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Doprava -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-category-title">Doprava</div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">Osobní vozidlo</span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value">12 Kč / km</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-row">
          <span class="pricing-row-label">Užitkové vozidlo</span>
          <span class="pricing-row-value">17 Kč / km</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    <p class="pricing-note"><sup>*</sup> <strong>Pohotovostní výjezd</strong> – výjezdy mimo pracovní dobu (Po–Pá 8–18), o víkendu a ve svátky. Výjezd je poskytnut do 2 hodin od příjmu pohotovostní objednávky.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #cenik { background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .pricing-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-card.featured { border-color: var(--color-accent); border-top: 3px solid var(--color-accent); }
  .pricing-category-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent-muted);
  }
  .pricing-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .pricing-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .pricing-row-label { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text); }
  .pricing-row-value {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .pricing-row-value.muted {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .pricing-row-label sup {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
  }
  .pricing-note {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    background: var(--color-brand-subtle);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pricing-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
